          </div>

          <div class="terms-section">
            <h2>Use of Our Services</h2>
            <h3>Permitted Uses</h3>
            <p>You may use our services to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Access information about our programs and services</li>
              <li>Register for events and volunteer opportunities</li>
              <li>Make donations to support our mission</li>
              <li>Subscribe to newsletters and updates</li>
              <li>Contact us with questions or feedback</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Prohibited Uses</h3>
            <p>You agree not to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Use our services for any unlawful purpose or in violation of these terms</li>
              <li>Interfere with or disrupt our services or servers</li>
              <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
              <li>Submit false or misleading information</li>
              <li>Use automated systems to access our services without permission</li>
              <li>Violate the rights of others or engage in harmful behavior</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="terms-section">
            <h2>Donations and Payments</h2>
            <p>All donations are voluntary and are used to support our charitable mission. By making a donation, you agree that:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Donations are made willingly and without expectation of goods or services in return</li>
              <li>All donations are final and non-refundable except as required by law</li>
              <li>You will receive a donation receipt for tax purposes where applicable</li>
              <li>We reserve the right to refuse donations that we determine are inappropriate</li>
              <li>Payment information is processed securely through our payment processor</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="terms-section">
            <h2>Volunteer Services</h2>
            <p>If you volunteer with our organization, you agree to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Provide accurate information in your volunteer application</li>
              <li>Comply with our volunteer policies and guidelines</li>
              <li>Maintain confidentiality of sensitive information</li>
              <li>Represent our organization in a professional manner</li>
              <li>Follow safety protocols and procedures</li>
              <li>Notify us promptly if you cannot fulfill volunteer commitments</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We reserve the right to decline volunteer applications or terminate volunteer relationships at our discretion.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="terms-section">
            <h2>Events and Programs</h2>
            <p>Participation in our events and programs is subject to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Available space and program capacity</li>
              <li>Meeting program eligibility requirements</li>
              <li>Compliance with event rules and guidelines</li>
              <li>Payment of applicable fees (if any)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We reserve the right to cancel or modify events and programs due to circumstances beyond our control. In such cases, we will provide reasonable notice and, where applicable, refunds.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="terms-section">
